data.description: Come home to this wonderful corner lot house Located in the Helotes area. All brick traditional front porch entrance welcomes you to this 4 bedroom 3.5 bath with a spare office space that was previously being used as a second master down. Large, Very High elegant ceilings and large windows allows all the natural light to enter in this spacious living room that is complete with an all wood/gas fireplace. Fully equipped kitchen with tall 42" cabinets complete with all stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and a gas range stove top. Full Master Suite w Luxury bath-his/hers walk in closet, garden tub and separate shower. Wooden large staircase leads to an upstairs with its full sized 2 bedrooms, game room an  entertainment/movie area. It has its own Water Softener, Dryer and Washer that the seller may be open to leaving and its Private fully fenced Backyard w/Covered Patio ready for those BBQ nights. Tuff Shed is also included. Beautiful and perfect home awaiting for you and your family. See you soon!
